snippet.title: BS Sutte Hakkun Event Version - Intro and Practice Stages.
snippet.description: Gameplay of the first of the three Satellaview Sutte Hakkun releases. the intro and the practice stages are the major differences from the Nintendo Power version (well, the NP Verson also allegedly has more levels, but aye.)
